{"tid":1697794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後香港人唔洗交五險一金同有戶口就可以隨便買中國大灣區樓","createTime":"2019-11-07T05:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T17:12:58.000Z","uid":104804,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0335713c57660bc0eef2929c612ef7f0308403e1","tid":1697794,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那人永遠都係下等人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n香港人反抗就快半年<br />\n你地中國共產黨仲要出政策奶我地鞋底<br />\n先唔理對香港人係唔係真係有用,有冇人真係想去大灣區買樓<br />\n但可以同你地中國人講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人真係又高貴過你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨便一隻警甴OT幾個月都可以炒高晒你地大灣區既樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得支那人諗盡辦法假結婚投資移民人才移民都想做香港人啦<br />\n<br />\n歡迎轉到微博我先唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2a2a7986ac9acea406ece9394ead0cf85de270","tid":1697794,"uid":59047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"仲唔快啲叫埋藍線親戚曱甴朋友上去買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acccd43c404e494e4a3688b6bbb7112d28912791","tid":1697794,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2a2a7986ac9acea406ece9394ead0cf85de270","tid":1697794,"uid":59047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"仲唔快啲叫埋藍線親戚曱甴朋友上去買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB